The area of the triangle with vertices 0, 4, and $3i$ is
\[\frac{1}{2} \cdot 4 \cdot 3 = 6.\]This area is also
\[\frac{1}{2} \cdot 5 \cdot h = \frac{5h}{2},\]so $h = \boxed{\frac{12}{5}}.$

